data.description: Welcome Home to 17008 Truax Ave. This beautiful 3 bedroom colonial is located on a peaceful and quiet dead end street, within seconds of Kamm's Corners. Plenty of shopping, dining, and amazing festivals all within walking distance make this home the perfect choice.  Totally remodeled in 2018, this home is ready for its new owners.  Furnace, Central Air, Updated Electrical, and a brand new kitchen highlight a long list of improvements.  All you have to do is turn the key!  Don't wait to tour it, or you will miss out on this gem in one of Cleveland's most desirable neighborhoods. Call your favorite Realtor and schedule your private showing today!!
